Stop all hadoop services.
Stop all Cloudera management services.
Ensure mysql connector jar is present in Cloudera manager server incase MySQL server is installed on a different server.
Make sure you have Cloudera manager console admin username and password.
Make sure you have the list of IP/hostname of all nodes in the cluster.
Make sure you have MySQL server IP/hostname and its root user credentials.
If using enterprise CDH,keep the Cloudera enterprise license ready and it might needed to reload the license after migration.
